title: Delicious
alt: I'm currently in the I Have Cheese phase of this cycle.
transcript:
[Frame is split by a diagonal.]
[First half: Cueball in front of open fridge.]
Cueball: I have leftover cheese. I should get chips and make nachos.[Second half: Cueball with bag of chips.]
Cueball: I have leftover chips. I should get cheese and make nachos.[Caption below the two drawings:]
A delicious cycle
